Dua Lipa, Future NostalgiaFuture Nostalgia is a breathtakingly fun, cohesive and ambitious attempt to find a place for disco in 2020.
Megan Thee Stallion, SugaSeasons change: every Hot Girl Summer must turn into a Mad As Hell Winter.
So Megan Thee Stallion chose the right moment to break free.
Her 9-song EP Suga drops just as the Houston rap goddess goes to war with her label 1501 Certified Entertainment.
While most rappers dream of making one song with potential to get radio play, Baby makes radio songs in his sleep.